headline: Fidelity Capital & Income Fund Q3 2024 Review
summary: For the quarter, the fund gained 3.63%, lagging the 5.28% advance of the benchmark, the ICE BofA US High Yield Constrained Index. Importantly, long-term performance remains quite favorable.
